name: Russ Gold's GitHub pages
tagline: Pages for Russell Gold on github
body:
### Welcome to My GitHub Pages.
Here you will find general information I maintain that is not tied explicitly to one of my projects. 

First of all, here are the [sample projects](maven-course-samples) for my _Getting Started with Apache Maven_ course. More will come.
